</head>
<body>
  <h1>Compare Author's Purpose</h1>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>ğŸ“˜ Text 1: "Welcome, Nelson!"</h2>
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To share information.</p>
    <button onclick="speak('Welcome, Nelson is written to share information about a celebration.')">ğŸ”Š Listen</button>
    <div class="hint-box">
