  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>ğŸŒ Text 2: "The World Is Your Family"</h2>
    <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To express opinion.</p>
    <button onclick="speak('The World Is Your Family is written to tell you what the author thinks about families around the world.')">ğŸ”Š Listen</button>
    <div class="hint-box">
