  <div class="section">
    <h3>ğŸ’¬ What makes a family?</h3>
    <textarea id="answer" rows="4" placeholder="Example: A family is people who love and help each other."></textarea>
    <div class="hint-box">
      ğŸ’¡ <strong>Hint:</strong> A family may include love, care, support, and being together. It is not only about being related by blood.
